article.headline: Wilkerson has 16 in Sam Houston's 60-56 win against UTEP
article.description: — Lamar Wilkerson had 16 points in Sam Houston's 60-56 victory over UTEP on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Wilkerson has 16 in Sam Houston's 60-56 win against UTEP
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- — Lamar Wilkerson had 16 points in Sam Houston's 60-56 victory over UTEP on Saturday night. Wilkerson added seven rebounds for the Bearkats (12-9, 5-1 Conference USA). Damon Nicholas Jr. added 11 points while finishing 5 of 10 from the floor to go with 13 rebounds. Davon Barnes added 11 points and seven rebounds. Tae Hardy led the way for the Miners (11-10, 2-4) with 13 points. Zid Powell added 10 points and three steals for UTEP. In addition, Calvin Solomon had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
